From grohol John Grohol Subject Re ATM writes TrueType font files are at least larger than their Type If you are using a disk compressor though be aware that TrueType fonts will compress whereas Type fonts will not they are encrypted This isn't entirely It is true that TrueType fonts are larger than their ATM counterparts but ATM fonts do get minimal Running Stacker report generator I get File Type Compression Ratio TrueType ATM ATM Metric Although the metric files are small they compress quite And as you can see even the regular files have some So doing the math on one such comparitive font file TTF Times bytes bytes compressed PFB Times bytes bytes Compressed You still win out even if the ATM Times font isn't Your mileage may vary depending on compression When heroes go down They go down fast John Grohol So don't expect any time to Center for Psychological Studies Equivocate the Nova Univ Lauderdale FL suzanne vega